title: Late At Zeit 4/19: Kid Cudi, Ron DeSantis, Johnny Depp, Libs of TikTok, Bill O'Reilly & Netflix
itunes:title: Late At Zeit 4/19: Kid Cudi, Ron DeSantis, Johnny Depp, Libs of TikTok, Bill O'Reilly & Netflix
description:
In this edition of Trends, Jack and Miles discuss Kid Cudi no longer having a relationship with Kanye West, Florida governor Ron DeSantis' targeting Disney with aims to remove their special status in the sate, Gen-Z's surprising support of Johnny Depp, a TikTok account that fuels the right-wing narrative that liberals are pedophiles, Bill O'Reilly's recent airport freakout and Netflix losing subscribers for the first time in a decade.
